{
  "video_id": "znSeL66e8qE",
  "title": "What if cracks in concrete could fix themselves? - Congrui Jin",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 7200.0,
      "end_time": 8840.0,
      "text": "Concrete is the most widely used"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 8840.0,
      "end_time": 10920.0,
      "text": "construction material in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 10920.0,
      "end_time": 13469.0,
      "text": "It can be found in swathes of city pavements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 13470.0,
      "end_time": 15980.0,
      "text": "bridges that span vast rivers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 15990.0,
      "end_time": 18220.0,
      "text": "and the tallest skyscrapers on earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 18220.0,
      "end_time": 19770.0,
      "text": "But this sturdy substance"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19770.0,
      "end_time": 21130.0,
      "text": "does have a weakness:"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 21130.0,
      "end_time": 22840.0,
      "text": "it’s prone to catastrophic cracking"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 22840.0,
      "end_time": 24540.0,
      "text": "that costs tens of billions of dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 24540.0,
      "end_time": 26130.0,
      "text": "to repair each year."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 26130.0,
      "end_time": 28290.0,
      "text": "But what if we could avoid that problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 28290.0,
      "end_time": 31310.0,
      "text": "by creating concrete that heals itself?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 31310.0,
      "end_time": 32769.0,
      "text": "This idea isn’t as far-fetched"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 32770.0,
      "end_time": 33920.0,
      "text": "as it may seem."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 33920.0,
      "end_time": 35763.0,
      "text": "It boils down to an understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 35763.0,
      "end_time": 37452.0,
      "text": "of how concrete forms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 37453.0,
      "end_time": 39243.0,
      "text": "and how to exploit that process"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 39243.0,
      "end_time": 40633.0,
      "text": "to our benefit."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 40648.0,
      "end_time": 42798.0,
      "text": "Concrete is a combination of coarse stone"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 42798.0,
      "end_time": 45146.0,
      "text": "and sand particles, called aggregates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 45146.0,
      "end_time": 47576.0,
      "text": "that mix with cement, a powdered blend"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 47576.0,
      "end_time": 49236.0,
      "text": "of clay and limestone."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 49245.0,
      "end_time": 51184.0,
      "text": "When water gets added to this mix,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 51185.0,
      "end_time": 52815.0,
      "text": "the cement forms a paste and"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 52815.0,
      "end_time": 55440.0,
      "text": "coats the aggregates, quickly hardening"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 55450.0,
      "end_time": 56275.0,
      "text": "through a chemical reaction"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 56275.0,
      "end_time": 58740.0,
      "text": "called hydration."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 58770.0,
      "end_time": 59937.0,
      "text": "Eventually, the resulting material"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 59937.0,
      "end_time": 62247.0,
      "text": "grows strong enough to prop up buildings"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 62247.0,
      "end_time": 63697.0,
      "text": "that climb hundreds of meters"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 63697.0,
      "end_time": 65137.0,
      "text": "into the sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 65137.0,
      "end_time": 66299.0,
      "text": "While people have been using"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 66299.0,
      "end_time": 68279.0,
      "text": "a variety of recipes to produce cement"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 68283.0,
      "end_time": 70283.0,
      "text": "for over 4,000 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 70283.0,
      "end_time": 71279.0,
      "text": "concrete itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 71279.0,
      "end_time": 73908.0,
      "text": "has a surprisingly short lifespan."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 73914.0,
      "end_time": 75624.0,
      "text": "After 20 to 30 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 75624.0,
      "end_time": 78574.0,
      "text": "natural processes like concrete shrinkage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 78574.0,
      "end_time": 80334.0,
      "text": "excessive freezing and thawing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 80334.0,
      "end_time": 83514.0,
      "text": "and heavy loads can trigger cracking."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 83514.0,
      "end_time": 85994.0,
      "text": "And it’s not just big breaks that count:"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 85994.0,
      "end_time": 88394.0,
      "text": "tiny cracks can be just as dangerous."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 88404.0,
      "end_time": 90440.0,
      "text": "Concrete is often used"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 90440.0,
      "end_time": 91464.0,
      "text": "as a secondary support"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 91464.0,
      "end_time": 93644.0,
      "text": "around steel reinforcements."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 93644.0,
      "end_time": 95854.0,
      "text": "In this concrete, even small cracks"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 95854.0,
      "end_time": 97944.0,
      "text": "can channel water, oxygen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 97944.0,
      "end_time": 100794.0,
      "text": "and carbon dioxide that corrode the steel"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 100794.0,
      "end_time": 103354.0,
      "text": "and lead to disastrous collapse."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 103354.0,
      "end_time": 105264.0,
      "text": "On structures like bridges and highways"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 105264.0,
      "end_time": 106934.0,
      "text": "that are constantly in use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 106934.0,
      "end_time": 108344.0,
      "text": "detecting these problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 108344.0,
      "end_time": 110163.0,
      "text": "before they lead to catastrophe"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 110164.0,
      "end_time": 112314.0,
      "text": "becomes a huge and costly challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 112314.0,
      "end_time": 113794.0,
      "text": "But not doing so"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 113794.0,
      "end_time": 116564.0,
      "text": "would also endanger thousands of lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 116564.0,
      "end_time": 119330.0,
      "text": "Fortunately, we’re already experimenting"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 119340.0,
      "end_time": 120354.0,
      "text": "with ways this material"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 120354.0,
      "end_time": 122124.0,
      "text": "could start fixing itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 122124.0,
      "end_time": 123374.0,
      "text": "And some of these solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 123374.0,
      "end_time": 124744.0,
      "text": "are inspired by concrete’s"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 124744.0,
      "end_time": 126854.0,
      "text": "natural self-healing mechanism."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 126859.0,
      "end_time": 129119.0,
      "text": "When water enters these tiny cracks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 129119.0,
      "end_time": 132109.0,
      "text": "it hydrates the concrete’s calcium oxide."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 132109.0,
      "end_time": 133979.0,
      "text": "The resulting calcium hydroxide"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 133979.0,
      "end_time": 136379.0,
      "text": "reacts with carbon dioxide in the air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 136379.0,
      "end_time": 137789.0,
      "text": "starting a process called"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 137789.0,
      "end_time": 139559.0,
      "text": "autogenous healing, where"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 139559.0,
      "end_time": 141819.0,
      "text": "microscopic calcium carbonate crystals"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 141819.0,
      "end_time": 144259.0,
      "text": "form and gradually fill the gap."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 144259.0,
      "end_time": 146159.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, these crystals"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 146159.0,
      "end_time": 148749.0,
      "text": "can only do so much, healing cracks"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 148749.0,
      "end_time": 151728.0,
      "text": "that are less than 0.3mm wide."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 151729.0,
      "end_time": 153589.0,
      "text": "Material scientists have figured out how"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 153589.0,
      "end_time": 155649.0,
      "text": "to heal cracks up to twice that size by"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 155649.0,
      "end_time": 158179.0,
      "text": "adding hidden glue into the concrete mix."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 158179.0,
      "end_time": 160690.0,
      "text": "If we put adhesive-filled fibers"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 160690.0,
      "end_time": 161559.0,
      "text": "and tubes into the mixture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 161559.0,
      "end_time": 164790.0,
      "text": "they’ll snap open when a crack forms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 164790.0,
      "end_time": 165939.0,
      "text": "releasing their sticky contents"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 165939.0,
      "end_time": 167509.0,
      "text": "and sealing the gap."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 167509.0,
      "end_time": 169469.0,
      "text": "But adhesive chemicals often behave"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 169469.0,
      "end_time": 170969.0,
      "text": "very differently from concrete,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 170969.0,
      "end_time": 172709.0,
      "text": "and over time, these adhesives"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 172709.0,
      "end_time": 175209.0,
      "text": "can lead to even worse cracks."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 175209.0,
      "end_time": 176899.0,
      "text": "So perhaps the best way to heal"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 176899.0,
      "end_time": 179590.0,
      "text": "large cracks is to give concrete"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 179590.0,
      "end_time": 181139.0,
      "text": "the tools to help itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 181139.0,
      "end_time": 182289.0,
      "text": "Scientists have discovered that"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 182289.0,
      "end_time": 183869.0,
      "text": "some bacteria and fungi"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 183879.0,
      "end_time": 185459.0,
      "text": "can produce minerals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 185459.0,
      "end_time": 187429.0,
      "text": "including the calcium carbonate"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 187429.0,
      "end_time": 189459.0,
      "text": "found in autogenous healing."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 189459.0,
      "end_time": 191690.0,
      "text": "Experimental blends of concrete"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 191690.0,
      "end_time": 193429.0,
      "text": "include these bacterial or fungal spores"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 193429.0,
      "end_time": 195979.0,
      "text": "alongside nutrients in their concrete mix,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 195979.0,
      "end_time": 197249.0,
      "text": "where they could lie dormant"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 197249.0,
      "end_time": 198999.0,
      "text": "for hundreds of years."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 198999.0,
      "end_time": 200329.0,
      "text": "When cracks finally appear"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 200329.0,
      "end_time": 202990.0,
      "text": "and water trickles into the concrete,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 202990.0,
      "end_time": 205209.0,
      "text": "the spores germinate, grow, and consume"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 205209.0,
      "end_time": 207429.0,
      "text": "the nutrient soup that surrounds them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 207429.0,
      "end_time": 209290.0,
      "text": "modifying their local environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 209290.0,
      "end_time": 210809.0,
      "text": "to create the perfect conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 210809.0,
      "end_time": 213259.0,
      "text": "for calcium carbonate to grow."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 213259.0,
      "end_time": 215328.0,
      "text": "These crystals gradually fill the gaps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 215329.0,
      "end_time": 216839.0,
      "text": "and after roughly three weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 216839.0,
      "end_time": 218219.0,
      "text": "the hard-working microbes"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 218219.0,
      "end_time": 219918.0,
      "text": "can completely repair cracks"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 219919.0,
      "end_time": 222699.0,
      "text": "up to almost 1mm wide."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 222699.0,
      "end_time": 223869.0,
      "text": "When the cracks seal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 223869.0,
      "end_time": 226490.0,
      "text": "the bacteria or fungi will make spores"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 226490.0,
      "end_time": 227569.0,
      "text": "and go dormant once more—"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 227569.0,
      "end_time": 229849.0,
      "text": "ready to start a new cycle of self-healing"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 229849.0,
      "end_time": 231279.0,
      "text": "when cracks form again."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 231689.0,
      "end_time": 232709.0,
      "text": "Although this technique"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 232709.0,
      "end_time": 234349.0,
      "text": "has been studied extensively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 234349.0,
      "end_time": 235689.0,
      "text": "we still have a ways to go"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 235689.0,
      "end_time": 236869.0,
      "text": "before incorporating it"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 236869.0,
      "end_time": 238909.0,
      "text": "in the global production of concrete."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 238963.0,
      "end_time": 241503.0,
      "text": "But, these spores have huge potential"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 241503.0,
      "end_time": 242403.0,
      "text": "to make concrete"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 242403.0,
      "end_time": 244683.0,
      "text": "more resilient and long-lasting—"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 244683.0,
      "end_time": 246162.0,
      "text": "which could drastically reduce"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 246163.0,
      "end_time": 248463.0,
      "text": "the financial and environmental cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 248463.0,
      "end_time": 249783.0,
      "text": "of concrete production."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 250303.0,
      "end_time": 252773.0,
      "text": "Eventually, these microorganisms"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 252773.0,
      "end_time": 254183.0,
      "text": "may force us to reconsider"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 254183.0,
      "end_time": 256123.0,
      "text": "the way we think about our cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 256123.0,
      "end_time": 258132.0,
      "text": "bringing our inanimate concrete jungles"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 258132.0,
      "end_time": 259243.0,
      "text": "to life."
    }
  ]
}